---
title: Cheesy Cherry Tomato Gnocchi with Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in cheese and baked until deliciously golden and oozy. Now, if that hasn’t got your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven.
